{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.1","label":"","reference":"Romains 13:1","prev_osis_id":"Rom.012.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.013.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Soumission aux autorit\u00e9s<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-7: cf. 1 Pi 2:13-17. Pr 24:21, 22. Lu 20:20-26.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.13.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    Que toute personne soit soumise aux autorit\u00e9s sup\u00e9rieures; car il n\u2019y a point d\u2019autorit\u00e9 qui ne vienne de Dieu, et les autorit\u00e9s qui existent ont \u00e9t\u00e9 institu\u00e9es de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.13","name":"Romains 13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.2","name":"Romains 13:2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.12.21","name":"Romains 12:21","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.12.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.2","label":"","reference":"Romains 13:2","prev_osis_id":"Rom.013.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.013.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.13.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi celui qui s\u2019oppose \u00e0 l\u2019autorit\u00e9 r\u00e9siste \u00e0 l\u2019ordre que Dieu a \u00e9tabli, et ceux qui r\u00e9sistent attireront une condamnation sur eux-m\u00eames.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.13","name":"Romains 13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.3","name":"Romains 13:3","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.1","name":"Romains 13:1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.3","label":"","reference":"Romains 13:3","prev_osis_id":"Rom.013.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.013.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.13.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Ce n\u2019est pas pour une bonne action, c\u2019est pour une mauvaise, que les magistrats sont \u00e0 redouter. Veux-tu ne pas craindre l\u2019autorit\u00e9? Fais le bien, et tu auras son approbation.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.13","name":"Romains 13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.4","name":"Romains 13:4","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.2","name":"Romains 13:2","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.4","label":"","reference":"Romains 13:4","prev_osis_id":"Rom.013.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.013.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.13.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Le magistrat est serviteur de Dieu pour ton bien. Mais si tu fais le mal, crains; car ce n\u2019est pas en vain qu\u2019il porte l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e, \u00e9tant serviteur de Dieu pour exercer la vengeance et punir celui qui fait le mal.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.13","name":"Romains 13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.5","name":"Romains 13:5","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.3","name":"Romains 13:3","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.5","label":"","reference":"Romains 13:5","prev_osis_id":"Rom.013.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.013.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.13.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Il est donc n\u00e9cessaire d\u2019\u00eatre soumis, non seulement par crainte de la punition, mais encore par motif de conscience.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.13","name":"Romains 13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.6","name":"Romains 13:6","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.4","name":"Romains 13:4","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.6","label":"","reference":"Romains 13:6","prev_osis_id":"Rom.013.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.013.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.13.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>C\u2019est aussi pour cela que vous payez les imp\u00f4ts. Car les magistrats sont des ministres de Dieu enti\u00e8rement appliqu\u00e9s \u00e0 cette fonction.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.13","name":"Romains 13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.7","name":"Romains 13:7","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.5","name":"Romains 13:5","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.7","label":"","reference":"Romains 13:7","prev_osis_id":"Rom.013.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.013.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.13.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Rendez \u00e0 tous ce qui leur est d\u00fb: l\u2019imp\u00f4t \u00e0 qui vous devez l\u2019imp\u00f4t, le tribut \u00e0 qui vous devez le tribut, la crainte \u00e0 qui vous devez la crainte, l\u2019honneur \u00e0 qui vous devez l\u2019honneur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.13","name":"Romains 13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.8","name":"Romains 13:8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.6","name":"Romains 13:6","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.8","label":"","reference":"Romains 13:8","prev_osis_id":"Rom.013.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.013.009,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Amour mutuel. Vigilance et puret\u00e9<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 8-10: cf. Mt 22:35-40. Ga 5:14. 1 Jn 3:11-23.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.13.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Ne devez rien \u00e0 personne, si ce n\u2019est de vous aimer les uns les autres; car celui qui aime les autres a accompli la loi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.13","name":"Romains 13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.9","name":"Romains 13:9","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.7","name":"Romains 13:7","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.9","label":"","reference":"Romains 13:9","prev_osis_id":"Rom.013.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.013.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.13.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>En effet, les commandements:<\/p>\n<p class=\"pi\">\n    Tu ne commettras point d\u2019adult\u00e8re, tu ne tueras point, tu ne d\u00e9roberas point, tu ne convoiteras point, et ceux qu\u2019il peut encore y avoir, se r\u00e9sument dans cette parole: Tu aimeras ton prochain comme toi-m\u00eame.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.13","name":"Romains 13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.10","name":"Romains 13:10","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.8","name":"Romains 13:8","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.10","label":"","reference":"Romains 13:10","prev_osis_id":"Rom.013.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.013.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"m\"><sup id=\"Rom.13.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>L\u2019amour ne fait point de mal au prochain: l\u2019amour est donc l\u2019accomplissement de la loi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.13","name":"Romains 13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.11","name":"Romains 13:11","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.9","name":"Romains 13:9","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.11","label":"","reference":"Romains 13:11","prev_osis_id":"Rom.013.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.013.012,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 11-14: cf. 1 Th 5:4-10. \u00c9p 5:3-18.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.13.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Cela importe d\u2019autant plus que vous savez en quel temps nous sommes: c\u2019est l\u2019heure de vous r\u00e9veiller enfin du sommeil, car maintenant le salut est plus pr\u00e8s de nous que lorsque nous avons cru.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.13","name":"Romains 13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.12","name":"Romains 13:12","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.10","name":"Romains 13:10","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.12","label":"","reference":"Romains 13:12","prev_osis_id":"Rom.013.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.013.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.13.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>La nuit est avanc\u00e9e, le jour approche. D\u00e9pouillons-nous donc des \u0153uvres des t\u00e9n\u00e8bres, et rev\u00eatons les armes de la lumi\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.13","name":"Romains 13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.13","name":"Romains 13:13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.11","name":"Romains 13:11","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.13","label":"","reference":"Romains 13:13","prev_osis_id":"Rom.013.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.013.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.13.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Marchons honn\u00eatement, comme en plein jour, loin des exc\u00e8s et de l\u2019ivrognerie, de la luxure et de l\u2019impudicit\u00e9, des querelles et des jalousies.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.13","name":"Romains 13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.14","name":"Romains 13:14","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.12","name":"Romains 13:12","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.14","label":"","reference":"Romains 13:14","prev_osis_id":"Rom.013.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Rom.014.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Rom.13.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Mais rev\u00eatez-vous du Seigneur J\u00e9sus-Christ, et n\u2019ayez pas soin de la chair pour en satisfaire les convoitises.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Rom.13","name":"Romains 13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.14.1","name":"Romains 14:1","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.14.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Rom.13.13","name":"Romains 13:13","id":"fra-LSG:Rom.13.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb50f0473.05008979');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb50f0473.05008979\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb50f0473.05008979","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb50f0473.05008979'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb50f0473.05008979\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}